        Decrypt a Message and download the blobs of the Message (e.g. image or file)
        Parameters:
        threemaId - Threema ID of the sender
        messageId - Message ID
        box - Encrypted box data of the file/image message
        nonce - Nonce that was used for message encryption
        outputFolder - Output folder for storing decrypted images/files
        Returns:
        result of message reception
